FULL LIQUOR TAVERN
Awesome service with a smile! That’s what you can expect at Uncle Fats Bar & Restaurant. From our management team to our expert staff, we promise to make your eating & drinking experience delicious, relaxing, and enjoyable. Our Bar setting, is casual and comfortable. Come as you are and meet your friends to watch the game and enjoy music. Our menu is full of yummy food that you will love. Be adventurous and get out of the house and have fun!
Uncle Fats Bar & Restaurant is located in the heart of Tampa Bay. We are open every day and we want to serve you! Please come on down and order our award winning hot wings. We also have a amazing happy hour where you can eat and drink on the cheap.
At Uncle Fats we love you!
